# ===== 编译产物 / 输出目录 =====
Project/Objects/
Project/Listings/
Project/build/
Project/DebugConfig/
OUT/

# ===== Keil 包缓存 / CMSIS 下载(体积大, 可由 Keil 包管理器还原) =====
Project/.pack/
Project/.cmsis/

# ===== Keil 用户 / GUI / 调试 临时文件 =====
*.uvguix.*
*.uvoptx
*.scvd
Project/*.log
Project/JLinkLog.txt
Project/JLinkSettings.ini
Project/.clang-format

# ===== 备份文件 / 目录 =====
*.bak
*.bak.gbk
*_backup_*/

# ===== 其它常见产物 =====
*.o
*.axf
*.bin
*.hex
*.crf
*.dep
*.lst
*.map

# ===== 编辑器 / 工具 =====
.vscode/
.claude/

# ===== Office 打开文档时的锁定临时文件 =====
~$*
